mixin modalSize 
  h5.mt-5 Modal Size
  p Modals have four optional sizes, available via modifier classes to be placed on a 
    code .modal-dialog
    |. These sizes kick in at certain breakpoints to avoid horizontal scrollbars on narrower viewports. The sizes are:
  
  .mt-3
    code .modal-xl
    |, 
    code .modal-lg
    |,  
    code .modal-sm
    |,  
    code .modal-xs
